\n|2015\n|''[[Limitless (TV series)|Limitless]]''\n|Lawrence Drake\n|Episode: \"Headquarters!\"\n|-\n|2016\n|''Charity Case''\n|Ronald\n|Television movie\n|-\n|2016\n|''[[Lucifer (TV series)|Lucifer]]''\n|Carmen\n|Episode: \"Wingman\"\n|-\n|2016\n|''[[Atlanta (TV series)|Atlanta]]''\n|Raleigh Marks\n|Episode: \"The Big Bang\"\n|-\n|2016\n|''Jay & Pluto''\n|Therapist\n|Unknown episodes\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[Elementary (TV series)|Elementary]]''\n|Jack Brunelle\n|Episode: \"Over a Barrel\"\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[Son of Zorn]]''\n|Robert\n|Episode: \"The Quest for Craig\"\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[Survivor's Remorse]]''\n|Samuel\n|4 episodes\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[The Mist (TV series)|The Mist]]''\n|Gus Redman/Gus Bradley\n|Recurring; 8 episodes\n|-\n|2017\n|''Thin Ice''\n|Bill\n|Television movie\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[She's Gotta Have It (TV series)|She's Gotta Have It]]''\n|Dog #10\n|Episode: \"#DaJumpoff (DOCTRINE)\"\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[Kevin Can Wait]]''\n|Jerry\n|Episode: \"Kevin Moves Metal\"\n|-\n|2018\n|''[[The Good Cop (American TV series)|The Good Cop]]''\n|Burl Loomis\n|10 episodes\n|-\n|TBA\n|''[[Your Honor (miniseries)|Your Honor]]''\n|Charlie\n|Upcoming miniseries\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Video games ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Year\n!Title\n!Role\n!Notes\n|-\n|2013\n|''[[Grand Theft Auto V]]''\n|The Local Population\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Official}}\n*{{IMDb name|926086}}\n*{{IBDB name}}\n*[http://www.lortel.org/LLA_archive/index.cfm?keyword=isiah+whitlock&COMMITT=YES&search_by=ALL&Go.x=0&Go.y=0 Isiah Whitlock Jr.] at the [[Internet Off-Broadway Database]]\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Whitlock, Isiah Jr.}}\n[[Category:1954 births]]\n[[Category:African-American male actors]]\n[[Category:American male film actors]]\n[[Category:American male stage actors]]\n[[Category:American male television actors]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Actors from South Bend, Indiana]]\n[[Category:Southwest Minnesota State University alumni]]\n[