on-theatre/news/andrew-lloyd-webbers-cinderella-delays-west-end_51104.html \"Andrew Lloyd Webber's ''Cinderella'' delays opening until October\"], WhatsOnStage.com, 5 March 2020</ref> \n|-\n|''[[City of Angels (musical)|City of Angels]]'' (revival)\n|{{flagicon|United Kingdom}} [[Garrick Theatre]], London, England\n|Closed until 31 May 2020.\n|<ref name=\"west end\" />\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Come from Away]]''\n|{{flagicon|United States}} [[Gerald Schoenfeld Theatre]], New York City, New York, U.S. \n|Closed until 7 June 2020.\n|<ref name=\"cnn\" />\n|-\n|{{flagicon|United Kingdom}} [[Phoenix Theatre, London|Phoenix Theatre]], London, England\n|Closed until 31 May 2020.\n|<ref name=\"west end\" />\n|-\n|''[[Company (musical)|Company]]'' (revival)\n|{{flagicon|United States}} [[Bernard B. Jacobs Theatre]], New York City, New York, U.S. \n|Postponed.\n|<ref name=\"cnn\" />\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Dear Evan Hansen]]''\n|{{flagicon|United States}} [[Music Box Theatre]], New York City, New York, U.S. \n|Closed until 7 June 2020.\n|<ref name=\"cnn\" />\n|-\n|{{flagicon|United Kingdom}} [[No\u00ebl Coward Theatre]], London, England\n|Closed until 31 May 2020.\n|<ref name=\"west end\" />\n|-\n|''[[Diana (musical)|Diana]]''\n|{{flagicon|United States}} [[Longacre Theatre]], New York City, New York, U.S. \n|Opening postponed.\n|<ref name=\"cnn\" />\n|-\n|''[[Endgame (play)|Endgame]]'' and ''[[Rough for Theatre II]]'' double bill\n|{{flagicon|United Kingdom}} [[Old Vic]], London, England\n|Closed two weeks ahead of its scheduled end date in March 2020\n|<ref name=\"oldvic01\">{{cite web|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/go/london/theatre/old-vic-endgame-coronavirus-daniel-radcliffe-a4387811.html|title=Old Vic becomes first London theatre to cancel performances as Endgame closes early amid coronavirus outbreak &#124; London Evening Standard|access-date=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Everybody's Talking About Jamie]]''\n|{{flagicon|United Kingdom}} [[Apollo Theatre]], London, Eng