 Vic becomes first London theatre to cancel performances as Endgame closes early amid coronavirus outbreak &#124; London Evening Standard|access-date=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Everybody's Talking About Jamie]]''\n|{{flagicon|United Kingdom}} [[Apollo Theatre]], London, England\n|Closed until 31 May 2020.\n|<ref name=\"west end\" />\n|-\n|''[[Flying Over Sunset]]''\n|{{flagicon|United States}} [[Vivian Beaumont Theatre]], New York City, New York, U.S. \n|Opening postponed.\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/03/lincoln-center-theater-postpones-broadway-flying-over-sunset-until-fall-1202891048/|title=Lincoln Center Theater Postpones Broadway\u2019s \u2018Flying Over Sunset\u2019 Until Fall|last=Evans|first=Greg|last2=Evans|first2=Greg|date=2020-03-24|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Frozen (musical)|Frozen]]''\n|{{flagicon|United States}} [[St. James Theatre]], New York City, New York, U.S. \n|Closed until 7 June 2020.\n|<ref name=\"cnn\" />\n|-\n|''[[Girl from the North Country (musical)|Girl from the North Country]]'' (revival)\n|{{flagicon|United States}} [[Belasco Theatre]], New York City, New York, U.S. \n|Closed until 7 June 2020.\n|<ref name=\"cnn\" />\n|-\n|''[[Hadestown]]''\n|{{flagicon|United States}} [[Walter Kerr Theatre]], New York City, New York, U.S. \n|Closed until 7 June 2020.\n|<ref name=\"cnn\" />\n|-\n|''[[Hairspray (musical)|Hairspray]]'' (revival)\n|{{flagicon|United Kingdom}} [[London Coliseum]], London, England\n|Postponed to 1 September to 8 November.\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.whatsonstage.com/london-theatre/news/hairspray-west-end-michael-ball-reschedule_51322.html|title=Hairspray in the West End with Michael Ball to reschedule run to autumn 2020 {{!}} WhatsOnStage|website=www.whatsonstage.com|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Hamilton (musical)|Hamilton]]''\n|{{flagicon|United States}} [[Richard Rodgers Theatre]], New York City, New York, U.S. 